       RECE64-NEXT-SEC            SECTION.
      *
           MOVE    ZERO          TO    FLG-RECE64
           READ    RECE64-FILE   NEXT
               AT  END
                   MOVE    1     TO    FLG-RECE64
           END-READ
           .
       RECE64-NEXT-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *****************************************************************
      *    中間ファイルＲＥＡＤ処理（Ｆ００５）
      *****************************************************************
       RECE65-NEXT-SEC            SECTION.
      *
           MOVE    ZERO          TO    FLG-RECE65
           READ    RECE65-FILE   NEXT
               AT  END
                   MOVE    1     TO    FLG-RECE65
           END-READ
           .
       RECE65-READ-EXT.
           EXIT.
